Meet Lin Wong:

"Hi , welcome to my website! I'm Lin Wong, an elearning designer and developer, developer, and consultant. While I work remotely, my company is proudly Australian, specialising in creating visual and brand-driven e-learning that delivers impactful learning experiences aligned with your brand identity."

Read more

Struggling to make your elearning effective?

At SW digital, we help you tackle these learning challenges that may resonate with you:

Ineffective and hard to absorb

Text-heavy content, complex processes, and dull design make learning difficult to engage with and apply.

Lacks brand identity and cohesion

Generic elearning doesnt reflect company culture, values, or aesthetics.

Accessibility and inclusivity are overlooked

Your elearning doesnt accommodate diverse learning needs, limiting engagement for diverse learners.

My strategies to addressing your challenges.

Ill help you achieve your learning goals with:

Breaking down complexity

Applying instructional design to transform intricate ideas into clear, digestible visuals and narrativesmaking information easier to understand and retain.

Branded elearning experience

Seamlessly integrating your brands identity through visuals, language, and storytelling to create a cohesive and memorable learning journey.

Effective and inclusive learning

Applying proven learning principles and accessibility standards to ensure engagement and usability for all learners.

Branded eLearning Development

Custom eLearning development tailored to your brandlogos, colours, and toneseamlessly integrated into your preferred authoring tool, whether Articulate Storyline, Rise, Evolve, or others.

Course Theme Design

Visually stunning eLearning themes designed in Figma. We create polished, brand-aligned course look and feel that enhance learner engagement.

Visual Assets Retracing

Upgrade outdated visuals with high-quality, professional retracing. Clear, polished graphics that align with your brand for a seamless learning experience.

Premium eLearning Templates

Ready-to-use, customisable templates designed for rapid development. Clean, professional, and compatible with leading eLearning tools.
